snippet.title: [Outdated UNDERTALE: Papyrus' BELIEF] Underevent Showcase
snippet.description:
Want to keep updated on Papyrus' BELIEF and my other projects? Join my newly opened Discord Server! https://discord.gg/6vG3qKpBeH

So guys, we did it. Papyrus' BELIEF got into UNDEREVENT! It took a lot of work but I'm so proud of the team for pulling through with me.

If you don't know what UNDEREVENT is then you can go check out the full showcase right now! https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TSOyg3n0GFM

All credits are within the video and thank you so much for the reception!
